description: Nakapepes is the third collection from Nakamotos on Bitcoin. This collection pays homage to the OG NFT project the Rare Pepe Project with a set of Pepe PFP's. Concluding the Nakamotos on Bitcoin Genesis art project of Satoshi Nakamoto the creator of Bitcoin, birthing the first ever NFT collection the Rare Pepe Project.
name: NakaPepes
